{
  "stem": "894.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I remember, at one point, one German woman leaning over and giving me a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I was trying to figure out what to do with my sister, because I really didn't want to lose her.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I told her I observed somebody doing that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Running off to-- to a-- what I mentioned before-- running off into an aisle-- into a-- alongside the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What do you call them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Alley.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had these little houses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a small town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had-- I cannot remember now the name of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] All these things were fresh in my memory after it happened, but, um, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember them for a very long time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somehow, lately, I don't remember a lot of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember saying to my sister, since you cannot-- and I don't want-- you cannot walk, and I don't want them to cart you off in a wheelbarrow and not know what happens to you, I am going to be on the lookout.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When I see an alley where I think it's safe, that the house is built so that it has, in the back, where you can run and-- and not be observed-- I will say 'now,' and we'll run.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we wanted to make sure-- they were going past that town, I didn't know what comes after and what opportunity will present itself again for-- for-- for running off like that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I remember looking and seeing a guard in the back of us, seeing one in the front of us, not seeing anybody right near us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember saying 'now,' and I started to run with my sister.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we ran to the back of the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we leaned down.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
